Lady Hawks scans showed Devilduer and Hurricanes approach, "State 
your name rank and faction." she exclaimed in a seemingly confident 
manner.

As a show of trust she transformed to full bot mode. Her talons 
transformed to three pronged daggers that she quickly placed in thier 
compartments on her legs. her wings folded around her in capelike 
fashion and the hawks head she'd had moments ago flipped behind her 
head resembling a crown. She appeared week but was ready to 
demonstrate her strength when and if necessary.
